(201, 1, 'Priyank Baby Girls'' Dress', '&lt;p&gt;A cherry is the fruit of many plants of the genus Prunus, and is a fleshy drupe. The cherry fruits of commerce usually are obtained from a limited number of species such as cultivars of the sweet cherry, Prunus avium.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Priyank Baby Girls'' Dress', '', ''),
(202, 1, 'Happy Kids Baby Walker with Music', '&lt;p&gt;Watermelon Kiran is sugary, juicy with a grainy texture. It is wealthy in electrolytes &amp; water. It brings more nutrients per calorie making it an outstanding health product. It is wealthy in photonutrients including anti-oxidant flavonoids. It is an excellent source of potassium &amp; manganese and it is an outstanding source of Vitamin A, includes a good amount of thiamin (vitamin B-1), vitamin-B6 (pyridoxine), and vitamin-C.Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce &amp; availability.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Happy Kids Baby Walker with Music', '', ''),
(203, 1, 'Toyhouse Radio Remote Control', '&lt;p&gt;Oranges are very sugary and juicy and considered to be the world''s best orange for fresh consumption because they are naturally juice, very sweet, seedless and peels and segments very easily. It includes a variety of phytochemicals including flavanoids hesperetin, carotenoids alpha and beta-carotene, etc. It is wealthy in Vitamin C, A and Folate and includes small amounts of Vitamin B &amp; E complex vitamins too. Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce &amp; availability.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Toyhouse Radio Remote Control', '', ''),
(204, 1, 'Batman Boys'' T-Shirt', '&lt;p&gt;Broccoli is a rich source of Vitamin A, B &amp; C and minerals such as magnesium, zinc and &quot;potassium&quot;. It is cholesterol-free and contains dietary fibre. Calories = 22. It aids in the prevention of certain types of &quot;cancer&quot; and in the regulation of cholesterol in the blood. It helps boost the immune system and increases bone health.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Broccoli is a common ingredient in Continental cuisine, popularly used in sauces. In Indian cuisine, it is used in curries, sabjis, stir fried vegetable dishes, soups and salads.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Batman Boys'' T-Shirt', '', ''),
(205, 1, 'Aarika Baby Girls'' Party Wear Frock', '&lt;p&gt;Kiwi fruit, also identified as Chinese gooseberry or Macaque peach, is the general fruit of China. The flesh in cross section is very fine-looking and beautiful. It is dazzling green in color, with frequent soft small ripe seeds. The fruit has a delicate savor with a pleasant smell. The sugary fruit flavors like a mixture of strawberry, pineapple and banana.Product image shown is for representation purpose only, the actually product may vary based on season, produce &amp; availability.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Aarika Baby Girls'' Party Wear Frock', '', ''),
(206, 1, 'AndAlso Blue Cat Push Along Car', '&lt;p&gt;Alphonso is a seasonal mango cultivar that is considered as one of the best in terms of sweetness, richness and flavor.It has considerable shelf life of a week after it is ripe making it exportable. It is also one of the most expensive kinds of mango and is grown mainly in western india. It is a seasonal fruit with each mango weighing between 150g and 300g each. This variety of mango has a very short season of about two months from the end of March till end May when the monsoon sets in the Konkan Region.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'AndAlso Blue Cat Push Along Car', '', ''),
